url: 'https://codex13.dev/student-dev-kit'
abstract: >-
  Codex 13 Student Dev Kit is a Windows installer that sets up a portable
  development environment for students in a user-selected folder without
  requiring administrator rights. It supports bilingual installation (Polish
  and English), multiple profiles (Start, Classroom), and portable installs
  of VS Code, Git for Windows, and XAMPP.
